snippet.title: Polymega Gameplays - Buttsubushi [PlayStation - PAL]
snippet.description:
Originally released in Japan, Buttsubushi is an action puzzle with puzzling actions. Addictive and challenging gameplay. Crush them before they crush you! A mind-bending 100 levels to clear. Multiplayer mode for up to 4 players. Buttsubushi offers a real challenge even to the most experienced puzzle fan.

Published by Phoenix Games
Developed by Selen
BIOS Used: Polymega BIOS
